is that if every time in the morning

00:00:23.800 --> 00:00:25.300
you put these things in order,

00:00:25.500 --> 00:00:27.100
absolutely in order,

00:00:27.400 --> 00:00:29.400
it would take you half an hour.

00:00:29.500 --> 00:00:30.500
