and I can't change their lives

00:00:38.100 --> 00:00:39.800
with a six or twelve lesson course.

00:00:40.200 --> 00:00:43.000
I can show them how to work themselves,

00:00:43.100 --> 00:00:44.300
how to go by,

00:00:44.700 --> 00:00:45.700
and that's what helps

00:00:45.800 --> 00:00:48.400
to give themselves further lessons,

00:00:48.400 --> 00:00:50.700
not to chat, try to change.

