OK, there is the violin,

00:00:54.000 --> 00:00:55.300
and turn it over,

00:00:55.500 --> 00:00:57.000
to play, turn this here

00:00:57.100 --> 00:00:57.900
and turn this over.

00:00:58.000 --> 00:00:58.900
If you do that,

