So, these are intervals

00:01:16.000 --> 00:01:18.000
If you do that you have no intervals.

00:01:18.300 --> 00:01:21.200
As a result, you lose the interval sense,

00:01:22.300 --> 00:01:25.900
you look at the music and it gives you notes

00:01:26.200 --> 00:01:28.200
and that's why you don't hear the music,

00:01:28.300 --> 00:01:30.000
that's why I can't go to the composer.

00:01:30.200 --> 00:01:32.000
You have to find out with the fingers,

00:01:32.100 --> 00:01:34.000
of what the composer is saying,

00:01:34.200 --> 00:01:36.200
because we are not free,

00:01:36.300 --> 00:01:38.200
because we want to do it with the bow.

00:01:38.235 --> 00:01:39.500
May I have your hand?

00:01:43.000 --> 00:01:45.300
You see, this is what the tendency is
Yes

