00:04:06.500 --> 00:04:07.900
What are, the names?

00:04:08.000 --> 00:04:10.500
G A B C D

00:04:10.600 --> 00:04:11.400
Thank you.

00:04:11.500 --> 00:04:13.300
What you say, G A B C D

00:04:13.400 --> 00:04:15.500
forget the G because it's an open string

00:04:16.000 --> 00:04:19.200
But it is... Can you say ABCD?

00:04:19.300 --> 00:04:20.100
ABCD

00:04:20.200 --> 00:04:22.800
Now, can you throw your hand out,

00:04:23.300 --> 00:04:26.000
in the shape of ABCD?

00:04:27.000 --> 00:04:28.100
That's right

00:04:28.500 --> 00:04:32.600
So, that's a whole step, half step
and a whole step, three intervals.

00:04:32.700 --> 00:04:34.000
Soften, soften

00:04:36.500 --> 00:04:37.300
That's right

00:04:37.900 --> 00:04:40.800
Now, if I say, G...

00:04:41.300 --> 00:04:44.400
A major, sixth position, G string

00:04:48.100 --> 00:04:50.100
...the thumb doesn't do anything

00:04:50.200 --> 00:04:53.100
The thumb comes here, attracts...

